author = {Raef A. Fadel and Mohamed Ramzi Almajed and Austin Parsons and Jasmeet Kalsi and Muthanna Shadid and Mohamed Maki and Mohammad Alqarqaz and Herb Aronow and Jennifer Cowger and Brittany Fuller and Tiberio Frisoli and Gillian Grafton and Henry Kim and Crystal Jones and Gerald Koenig and Akshay Khandelwal and Hassan Nemeh and Brian O’Neill and Daizo Tanaka and Celeste Williams and Pedro Villablanca and William O’Neill and Khaldoon Alaswad and Mir Babar Basir},
